description: Serving up downtown Silver Spring with a delicious fusion of Venezuelan & Mexican cuisines, is Chef Molivia in her super sleek Fajita Sub Factory. Faring from Venezuela herself, this Chef is bringing her passion for food, service, and quality ingredients to her every dish, and thus her authentic tacos, subs, and arepas, etc... are all so delicious, her entire menu has become local legend. If you’re looking for grub that’s made with much love, make your way straight to the Fajita Sub Factory, and say a friendly “Hey!” to Chef Molivia today!
name: Fajita Sub Factory
